{"tid":827040,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"Jackson Wang同Kris Wu邊個先係中國最成功嘅Rapper?","createTime":"2018-09-18T16:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-19T08:23:37.000Z","uid":193951,"like":33,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f4e2aa218f7a625aaad83d6ae89c6a940e8d84f0","tid":827040,"uid":193951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-18T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"香港代表:前香港男子劍擊代表隊隊員、當紅韓團GOT7成員。於2017年8月26日通過全英文單曲《Papillon》正式以歌手身份在中國Solo出道。在中國 Billboard 的 China V 曾經以《 Dawn Of Us 》連續六週拿下第一名，並在全球新興人氣歌手榜上拿下第 14 名。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/225708_8b422f4110588a9a428ce579d0c16532.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F225708_8b422f4110588a9a428ce579d0c16532.gif&h=138b3e5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/17/225734_b0daaacaf337a6383a037b631685c80c.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F17%2F225734_b0daaacaf337a6383a037b631685c80c.gif&h=5e7cd815&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/19/000029_fc5ebdfd0bf68671abf1741d498fc710.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F19%2F000029_fc5ebdfd0bf68671abf1741d498fc710.gif&h=62861b37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-sJp9E3zIY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR-sJp9E3zIY&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=a7cc7353\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R-sJp9E3zIY</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BBVLj_PSsZ8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DBBVLj_PSsZ8&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6a657172\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BBVLj_PSsZ8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4xN-jUfJAyM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D4xN-jUfJAyM&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=70bdb0b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=4xN-jUfJAyM</a><br />\n<br />\n加拿大代表:前韓團EXO成員。2017年10月發行的第二張英文單曲《Deserve》，在美國iTunes總榜及分榜皆拿下冠軍。2018年5月，發行新專輯的首張單曲《Like That》，在美國iTunes總榜及分榜再度拿下冠軍，並持續登頂72小時，以及登上Billboard Hot 100榜的第73位，以上皆打破華人歌手在榜的最佳紀錄。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/235558_f78492f0513c659e69dab2e47f567202.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F235558_f78492f0513c659e69dab2e47f567202.gif&h=1756308d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/235817_1f8d92c147ca0f526a729ef8c1b03b54.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F235817_1f8d92c147ca0f526a729ef8c1b03b54.gif&h=d382f246&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/18/235942_7fbe2b7653ad5fedb97f80808131b442.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F18%2F235942_7fbe2b7653ad5fedb97f80808131b442.gif&h=073dbb41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R4T43PncyQc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR4T43PncyQc&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=e0b9a30c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R4T43PncyQc</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pCdWnY4Dn2w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DpCdWnY4Dn2w&d=8w4Rztlu%2FXTBsuJOe601sMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=657b6212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pCdWnY